{"tid":1390834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲！立即停止和理非送頭行動","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:02:07.000Z","uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"147b2646098079caa3515c39eb5966096fcfac12","tid":1390834,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"而家多次大型示威活動 已經畀黑警同埋鄉黑知道你班人係冇反抗力，只係和理非式送頭！<br />\n<br />\n呢種和理非式送頭行動，示人以弱，只會激發黑警更強更大嘅暴力！<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日見到黑警用真槍指嚇市民，同埋電召黑社會用極度危險嘅火箭煙花射擊市民，就知道佢哋已經將示威者非人化， 並標籤成曱甴！<br />\n<br />\n咁下一步絕對好快就會出現對曱甴般嘅示威者（佢哋認為）實施屠殺！<br />\n<br />\n所以呢啲是示弱嘅示威行動，應該立即停止，不能再助長黑警同黑社會嘅法西斯主義."},{"pid":"f1d4aec9416f167570d85bd7035a76773717c315","tid":1390834,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT1vED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkT1vED.png&h=0accd33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d74a864269ce154b27d6d9111331885dab1f2fbb","tid":1390834,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:57:40.000Z","msg":"我知道好多企喺前面衝擊嘅示威者，其實本質係和理非，潛意識希望用不反抗運動嚟感召對方， 更甚者有啲係自殺、自暴自棄， <br />\n<br />\n最大問題咁嘅示威方式，係會引起對方更恐怖嘅暴力，以至下一輪嘅大規模開槍屠殺！"},{"pid":"00e9e2e64489020ade32887a96b231b0067035af","tid":1390834,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201